---
/** PodcastCarousel — placeholder until first three episodes exist.
 *  Addendum §7. CMS-editable carousel to live here. */
---

<section class="w-full">
  <div class="max-w-[1232px] mx-auto px-8 py-16">
    <p class="uppercase text-sm font-medium tracking-[2px] text-dark">From the podcast</p>
    <div class="border-t border-accent mt-4"></div>

    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8 mt-12 items-end">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h2 class="font-heading font-medium text-[48px] sm:text-[56px] leading-tight tracking-tight text-dark">
          Owners, suppliers, and what actually goes on behind the bar.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:w-[440px] shrink-0">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-dark">
          Every week I sit down with someone in the trade and we get into the stuff that doesn't make the brochure, the decisions that went well and the ones that cost a fortune.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Placeholder carousel cards — 3 slots, CMS-fed once live -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-12">
      <div class="bg-light-gray rounded-lg p-8 flex flex-col aspect-[4/5] border border-dashed border-dark/20">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-dark/40">Episode 01, coming soon</p>
        <p class="font-heading font-medium text-2xl text-dark/60 mt-4 leading-tight">First episode pending</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-dark/50 mt-auto">Launching shortly.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-light-gray rounded-lg p-8 flex flex-col aspect-[4/5] border border-dashed border-dark/20">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-dark/40">Episode 02, coming soon</p>
        <p class="font-heading font-medium text-2xl text-dark/60 mt-4 leading-tight">Second episode pending</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-dark/50 mt-auto">Launching shortly.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-light-gray rounded-lg p-8 flex flex-col aspect-[4/5] border border-dashed border-dark/20">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-dark/40">Episode 03, coming soon</p>
        <p class="font-heading font-medium text-2xl text-dark/60 mt-4 leading-tight">Third episode pending</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-dark/50 mt-auto">Launching shortly.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
